data.title: Peninsula Genealogical Society
data.text:
19 Jun 2009 - Sue & Bob HOHNEKE's pictures of some of Sec. 3 (13 Jun 2009) linked.

13 Jul 2009 - Ginny HAEN's pictures of all of Section 5 (13 Jun 2009) linked.

27 Jul 2009 - Sue HOHNEKE's and daughter Becky JACOBS' pictures of more of Section 3 (2 Jul 2009) linked.

4 Aug 2009 - Additional information added to a couple of stones in Section 5-Ginny HAEN (13 Jun 2009).

18 Aug 2009-Sue & Bob HOHNEKE's pictures of some of Sec. 3 taken 17 Aug 2009 linked.

24 Aug 2009-Sue & Bob HOHNEKE's pictures of some of Sec. 3 taken 19 Aug 2009 linked.

3 Sep 2009-TUCK Family Plot pictures in Sec. 2 taken by Sue and Bob HOHNEKE for John HEINTZELMAN-descendant-on 3 Sep 2009 linked to index.

22 Nov 2009 - Obituary for Mrs. Ole C. ERICKSON (Phyllis HEILMANN)-DC Adv.-15 Jul 1921 was added to her entry on this index.

4, 6, 12 Feb 2010 - OBITS added.

8 Feb 2010 - End of Sec. 3 -pictures by Sue & Bob HOHNEKE linked to index.

1-3 Mar 2010 - Section 2 (and part of Section 1?) and (1) picture from Sec. 4-digital pictures by Ginny HAEN linked to this index.

3 Mar 2010 - part of Sec. 4 pictures taken by Sue and Bob HOHNEKE on 2 Sep 2009 linked to this index.

6 Mar 2010 - part of Sec. 4 pictures taken by Sue and Bob HOHNEKE on 3 Sep 2009 linked to this index.

7 Mar 2010 - the end of Sec. 4 pictures taken by Sue and Bob HOHNEKE on 7 Sep 2009 linked to this index.

12 Mar 2010-Death certif. information added to DEHOS, Margaretha because bottom of stone says: Dau. of... (rest buried).

13 Apr, 6 May 2010-OBIT added

10 May 2010-correction to Maria C. SCHAFER's surname sent to us by Tim MANN who is researching the STEPHAN and DEHOS families.

14 Jul 2010-Section 1 begun by Sue and Bob HOHNEKE on 12 Jul 2010 with pictures linked.

22-23 Jul 2010 - Rest of Section 1 pictures taken by Sue and Bob HOHNEKE on 20 Jul 2010 being linked - CEMETERY INDEX & PHOTO SURVEY NOW COMPLETE.

9 Sep 2010 - OBIT added for Robert KELLER.

9 Oct 2010 - OBIT added

9 Apr 2011 - Esther Barbara WAGNER added from OBIT-Forbes Funeral Home.

15 Apr 2011 - Clyde L. ROBILLARD added from OBIT-HUEHNS Funeral Home.
